SMOz Version 0.2 README

== 1. Introduction ==
    Welcome to SMOz (Start Menu organizer). SMOz is a tool that can
  assist you in the organization of Windows start menu. SMOz provides
  an intuitive interface to manipulate the start menu (with unlimited 
  Undo/Redo). In addition, SMOz provides support for templates, which
  allow you to automate the manipulation of start menu.

== 2. System Requirements ==
    SMOz will run on any platform that supports .NET Framework v2.0

